# Gmail OAuth2 credentials — required to use the email_send tool
# Setup guide: https://developers.google.com/gmail/api/quickstart/nodejs
#
# Step 1: Go to Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials
# Step 2: Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Desktop app type)
# Step 3: Enable the Gmail API for your project
# Step 4: Use the OAuth Playground (https://developers.google.com/oauthplayground)
#         to generate a refresh token with scope: https://mail.google.com/
#
GMAIL_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com
GMAIL_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here
GMAIL_REFRESH_TOKEN=your_refresh_token_here
GMAIL_FROM=you@gmail.com

# Optional: custom path for the SQLite database (defaults to ./data/sales.db)
# DB_PATH=/custom/path/to/sales.db
